author: IGN
description:
Take a look at the Announcement Trailer for Is This Seat Taken?, a casual relaxing logic puzzle game developed by Poti Poti Studio. Players will need to find the perfect spot to seat people with clashing quirks before advancing to the next level. Take note of the unique aspects present in the people around a crowded movie theater, a wedding reception, or even a cramped taxi cab to suit everyone's needs. Is This Seat Taken? is coming soon to iOS, Android, macOS, and PC (Steam) with a demo releasing at a later date.

#IsThisSeatTaken #Gaming #IGN
title: Is This Seat Taken? - Official Announcement Trailer

author: IGN
description: Check out action-packed gameplay, weapons, characters, and upgrades in this Sodaman trailer for the upcoming bullet-heaven roguelike game. Sodaman will be available in Steam Early Access on February 17, 2025. Join Sodaman to free all the Sodas! Sodaman is a bullet-heaven roguelike game where you play as a supersoldier fighting against the alien hoards with his soda powers. Unlock new weapons, sodas, cybernetics, and more. But first, crack open a cold one.
title: Sodaman - Official Release Date Gameplay Trailer

author: IGN
description:
Take a look at the 'Get Tickets Now' Trailer for Captain America: Brave New World, in theaters on February 14 in IMAX.

In Captain America: Brave New World, Sam finds himself in the middle of an international incident after meeting with newly elected U.S. President Thaddeus Ross. He must discover the reason behind a nefarious global plot before the true mastermind has the entire world seeing red.

Captain America: Brave New World stars Anthony Mackie, Danny Ramirez, Shira Haas, Carl Lumbly, Xosha Roquemore, with Giancarlo Esposito, Liv Tyler, Tim Blake Nelson, and Harrison Ford. The film is directed by Julius Onah and produced by Kevin Feige and Nate Moore. Louis D’Esposito and Charles Newirth serve as executive producers. The screenplay is by Rob Edwards and Malcolm Spellman & Dalan Musso and Julius Onah & Peter Glanz, with story by Rob Edwards and Malcolm Spellman & Dalan Musson.

#CaptainAmericaBraveNewWorld #Marvel #IGN
title: Captain America: Brave New World - Official 'Get Tickets Now' Teaser Trailer (2025) Anthony Mackie

description:
Take a look at the Reveal Trailer for Vaultbreakers, a top-down PvPvE action RPG developed by BetaDwarf. Players will engage in epic brawls alone or with friends to complete dangerous missions across a dynamic fantasy world. Choose from various Champions, unlock perks, craft items, and awaken Artifacts to tailor your abilities and enhance your gameplay. Vaultbreakers is coming soon to PC (Steam) with a playtest available now.

There are nine legendary weapons to find in the Elden Ring base game, and once you have them all, you earn a fancy trophy or achievement for your efforts. Here’s how to find them all. Note: Shadow of the Erdtree is not required.

0:00 - Ruins Greatsword
0:30 - Grafted Blade Greatsword
1:13 - Sword of Night and Flame
2:25 - Marais Executioner’s Sword
3:33 - Bolt of Gransax
4:50 - Eclipse Shotel
5:09 - Golden Order Greatsword
6:36 - Devourer’s Scepter
7:55 - Dark Moon Greatsword
